  'rx054':{ uses:'Treats major depression, generalized anxiety disorder, fibromyalgia, diabetic nerve pain, and chronic musculoskeletal pain.', works:'SNRI antidepressant that increases both serotonin and norepinephrine levels in the brain to improve mood and reduce pain perception.', side:'Nausea (especially initially), dry mouth, fatigue, dizziness, constipation, sweating, sexual dysfunction.', warn:'Do not stop suddenly — taper dose gradually. May increase blood pressure. Avoid with MAO inhibitors. Serotonin syndrome risk.' },
