  'rx058':{ uses:'Treats enlarged prostate (BPH) to improve urinary flow and relieve urinary symptoms. Also treats male pattern hair loss (at lower doses).', works:'Inhibits 5-alpha reductase enzyme that converts testosterone to DHT — the hormone that stimulates prostate and hair follicle growth.', side:'Decreased sexual desire, erectile dysfunction, reduced ejaculate volume, breast tenderness.', warn:'Pregnant women must not handle crushed or broken tablets (can affect male fetus). PSA blood test results will be lower while on this medication.' },
