  'rx065':{ uses:'Treats nerve pain (neuropathy, shingles pain), epilepsy, and restless leg syndrome. Starting dose for gradual titration.', works:'Anticonvulsant that reduces the release of excitatory neurotransmitters, calming overactive nerve signals.', side:'Dizziness, drowsiness, loss of coordination, weight gain, memory difficulties.', warn:'Do not stop suddenly — can worsen seizures. May impair driving. Risk of misuse — take exactly as prescribed.' },
