  'rx067':{ uses:'Controls blood sugar levels in type 2 diabetes mellitus as part of diet and exercise management.', works:'Sulfonylurea that stimulates the pancreatic beta cells to release more insulin to lower blood glucose.', side:'Low blood sugar (hypoglycemia), weight gain, dizziness, nausea, stomach upset.', warn:'Carry glucose tablets or juice in case of low blood sugar. Take with breakfast. Monitor blood sugar regularly.' },
