  'rx069':{ uses:'Treats schizophrenia and Tourette syndrome. Also used for acute agitation and severe behavioral problems.', works:'Typical antipsychotic that blocks dopamine D2 receptors in the brain to reduce psychotic symptoms.', side:'Muscle stiffness and rigidity, restlessness (akathisia), tardive dyskinesia (with long-term use), drowsiness.', warn:'Long-term use can cause irreversible involuntary movements (tardive dyskinesia). Regular neurological monitoring required.' },
