  'rx071':{ uses:'Treats high blood pressure and fluid retention from heart or kidney disease.', works:'Thiazide diuretic that increases urine production and reduces blood volume to lower blood pressure.', side:'Low potassium (muscle cramps), frequent urination, sun sensitivity, dizziness, increased blood sugar.', warn:'Monitor potassium levels. Take in the morning. Use sunscreen. May increase uric acid — avoid if gout-prone.' },
  'rx072':{ uses:'Treats high blood pressure and edema (fluid retention). Standard thiazide diuretic dose.', works:'Increases urine output by blocking sodium reabsorption in the kidneys, reducing fluid volume.', side:'Low potassium, frequent urination, dizziness, sun sensitivity, elevated blood sugar.', warn:'Monitor potassium and kidney function. Drink adequate water. Take in morning to avoid nighttime urination.' },
