  'rx074':{ uses:'Treats adrenal insufficiency (Addison\'s disease), severe allergic reactions, and certain inflammatory conditions requiring internal steroids.', works:'Systemic corticosteroid hormone replacement that regulates inflammatory pathways and immune function throughout the body.', side:'Weight gain, increased blood sugar, mood changes, insomnia, stomach upset, bone thinning with long-term use.', warn:'Do not stop suddenly after prolonged use — taper as directed. Monitor blood sugar. Take with food to protect stomach.' },
